data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Covington, GA! A Gorgeous 4 BR / 2.5 BA with a wide open floorplan & a spacious, level backyard. The main living area reveals a cozy family room with a fireplace and it opens up to a Huge Chefs Dream Kitchen, & large centered island and an additional sitting area that's perfect for entertaining. Sep Dining area that compliments the kitchen and a formal living room space. The Owner Suite is the MASTER PIECE of this home.  It's Absolutely STUNNNING, w/ windows galore, tray ceilings, and an oversized walk-in closet. The master bath features a very large soaking tub, a separate walk-in shower, & double vanities. This dream home has a separate laundry room and multiple oversized bedrooms on the opposite side of the home which both open to a Jack & Jill full bathroom.  This gem is located in prime convenience to all your essential amenities, including hospitals, grocery stores, restaurants, charming downtown Covington Square, and more. Don't let this one get away!
